    <iconUrl>https://numerics.net/images/ExtremeNugetLogo.png</iconUrl>
    <description>Numerics.NET is a set of libraries for numerical computing and data analysis.

      This package provides a complete implementation of linear algebra functionality for arbitrary numerical types.

Supports .NET 6.0-9.0+, .NET Framework 4.62+, .NET Standard 2.0, and .NET Core 3.1 on Windows, Linux and Mac.</description>
    <summary>Numerics.NET Generic Numerics Library.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>Optimized symmetric tridiagonal eigenvalues and eigenvectors.</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright © 2004-2025, ExoAnalytics Inc. All rights reserved.</copyright>
    <tags>math statistics probability machine learning ml numerics linear algebra matrix vector solve optimization curve fit model fft integration differentiation interpolation regression generic</tags>
